channel.title: Error port forwarding
channel.description: for 5 days now i have been trying out ways to port forward. i finally got onto my router on the computer its hooked up to and added port 43594 to it and did everything right, it finished applying. i added my laptop ip address as the ip for the port forward and it wont let other people connect, i have my no-ip open, when people go to connect to it with port 43594 and my ip e.g triplescape.no-ip.biz it doesn't work, please help, iv been trying for a long time now. thankyou for reading
